## Задача: P1 — Command injection + Kill session

### 1. Command injection в /api/command
POST /api/command выполняет `execSync(req.body.command)` без санитизации. CWE-78.
 Любой может выполнить любую команду на сервере.

### Что исправить:

**Backend — routes/command.js:**
Добав command allowlist. Only allow safe commands:
- `bd *` (Beads commands)
- `git status`, `git log`, `git diff`
- `ls`, `cat`, `pwd`
- `node --version`, `npm --version`
- `openclaw *` (OpenClaw commands)

```javascript
// ... at top of file
const ALLOWED_COMMANDS = [
  /^bd\s/,
  /^git\s+(status|log|diff|branch)/,
  /^ls\b/,
  /^cat\b/,
  /^pwd\b/,
  /^node\s+--version/,
  /^npm\s+--version/,
  /^openclaw\s+/,
];

router.post('/', async (req, res) => {
  const { command } = req.body;

  if (!command) {
    return res.status(400).json({ error: 'command required' });
  }

  // Validate command against allowlist
  const isAllowed = ALLOWED_COMMANDS.some(pattern => pattern.test(command));
  if (!isAllowed) {
    return res.status(403).json({ error: 'Command not allowed', command });

  try {
    const output = execSync(`cd ${WORKSPACE} && ${command} 2>&1`, {
      timeout: 30000,
      maxBuffer: 1024 * 1024
    }).toString();
    res.json({ ok: true, output });
  } catch (error) {
    res.status(500).json({ ok: false, error: error.message, output: error.stdout?.toString() || '' });
  }
});
```

